Going back to the example provided by the OP, it appears the generated JSON schema output is using a bad reference. The "#" ref isn't rooted correctly (i.e. it's pointing to the `schema` node, not the root of the entire JSON document):

```
"PropertyB": {
    "type": "array",
    "items": { "$ref": "#/properties/PropertyA/items" }
}
